<DATELINE>
   WASHINGTON
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
US OFFICIALS yesterday offered an olive branch to North Korea ahead of next
week's talks at the United Nations on North Korea's withdrawal from the
nuclear non-proliferation treaty.
Mr Robert Gallucci, assistant secretary of state for political-military
affairs, told a Senate committee yesterday that the US would be willing to
